  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "thesis",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "10 - Patterns and Theses/Thesis - Historical Continuity of Air Force Position 1952 to 2026.md",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -600,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "legend",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Historical continuity 1952 to 2026\n\nThe Air Force institutional position on UAP has been ==remarkably stable for 70+ years==:\n\n- Phenomena are real\n- Observers are credible\n- Foreign or ET origin is not supported\n- Sustained attention warranted\n- No premature conclusion\n\nThis canvas shows the canonical incidents and source documents that anchor each decade.",
      "x": -1300,
      "y": -600,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 500,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "era1950s",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 1947-1955\nProject Sign, Grudge, Blue Book era. Foundational case record.",
      "x": -900,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "era1980s",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 1980s-1990s\nState Department channel reports of unidentified high-altitude/high-speed activity.",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "era2010s",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 2014-2019\nNimitz/Tic Tac era (not in this collection). Navy publishes mandatory reporting guidance 2019.",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "era2020s",
