    {
      "id": "samford-quote",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 1952 (Samford)\n\n==Credible observers are reporting the incredible.==\n\n==The Air Force views the flying saucers as a threat only because they are not understood and they are sufficiently frequent.==\n\n==The possibility [of man-made or controlled origin] was remote and not to be seriously considered.==",
      "x": -900,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "aaro-quote",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 2024-2026 (AARO public posture)\n\nReal phenomenon. Frequent enough to warrant institutional attention. Correlated radar and pilot observation. ==No demonstrated foreign or hostile origin.== No resolved explanation. Sustained collection effort.\n\nFunctionally identical to 1952 Samford position.",
      "x": 1200,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
